'Et voilà... et me voici...' he said with an infantile little whine in his voice. 'Un pauvre bonhomme qu'on traîne en prison. Oh, I don't want to go at all! Adam, isn't there anything that can be done? Think up something, please! Je suis souffrant, je suis en détresse. I shall confess I had been preparing a coup d'état if they start torturing me.'

